## v1.2.0 — 2026-04-19

**Amendment**: Added ProjectMnemosyne direct-execution verification data.

- Added "Direct execution (no script) is valid when" guidance block to When to Use
- Expanded Scale reference table with Time column and direct-execution row:
  - 14 worktrees, 4 dirty (`.coverage` only), ~2 min, 41 branches preserved
  - `git remote prune origin` cleaned 28+ stale remote tracking refs in the same pass
- Expanded Verified On table: added second ProjectMnemosyne row for direct-execution session
  (PRs #1221–#1255 all merged, no `--force` needed after removing `.coverage` artifacts)

## v1.1.0 — 2026-04-12

**Amendment**: Added ProjectMnemosyne generate-only verification row.

- Added Verified On row: 14 worktrees, generate-only mode, bash -n syntax checked
- Expanded Scale reference table with 14-worktree entry

## v1.0.0 — 2026-04-12

**Initial creation**: Worktree cleanup under user constraints (no branch deletion, script-first).

- Documented classify → script → hand-off → verify workflow
- 36 ProjectScylla worktrees; identified circuit-breaker real work in merged-branch worktree
- Established 4-phase workflow with 7-section reviewable script pattern
